[00:00.40]	[Near Misenum.,]
[00:01.22]	[Flourish. Enter POMPEY and MENAS at one door,
[00:01.63]	+ with drum and trumpet: at another, OCTAVIUS CAESAR,
[00:02.04]	+ MARK ANTONY, LEPIDUS, DOMITIUS ENOBARBUS, MECAENAS,
[00:02.45]	+ with Soldiers marching]
